msgid ""
"`Connection` represents an open database connection returned by "
"`ptool.db.connect()`."
msgstr ""
"`Connection` representa una conexión de base de datos abierta devuelta por "
"`ptool.db.connect()`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/db.md:57
msgid "It is implemented as a Lua userdata."
msgstr "Está implementada como userdata de Lua."

