msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.db.Connection:transaction`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/db.md:181
msgid "`db:transaction(fn)` runs `fn(tx)` inside a database transaction."
msgstr ""
"`db:transaction(fn)` ejecuta `fn(tx)` dentro de una transacción de base de "
"datos."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/db.md:183
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/db.md:183"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "Comportamiento:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/db.md:185
msgid "If `fn(tx)` returns normally, the transaction is committed."
msgstr "Si `fn(tx)` devuelve normalmente, la transacción se confirma."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/db.md:186
msgid ""
"If `fn(tx)` raises an error, the transaction is rolled back and the error is "
"re-raised."
msgstr ""
"Si `fn(tx)` produce un error, la transacción se revierte y el error se "
"vuelve a lanzar."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/db.md:188
msgid "Nested transactions are not supported."
msgstr "No se admiten transacciones anidadas."

